label: CatalogNumber
definition: A unique identifier for a unit within a catalog.

label: CollectorsText
definition: A text describing the collector(s), in any chosen format.
examples:
''Ex. 1.'' Peter Andersson
''Ex. 2.'' Peter Andersson, Anne Andersson
''Ex. 3.'' P. Andersson

label: FeatureObservationText
definition: A text describing the observation, in any chosen format.

label: FeatureObservationTypeName
definition: The name of a defined FeatureObservationType.

label: IdentificationText
definition: A text describing a single Identification (including e.g. taxon name, identified by, and identification date), in any chosen format.

label: LocalityText
definition: A text describing where the Occurrence took place, in any chosen format.
examples:
''Ex. 1.'' Frescati
''Ex. 2.'' Frescati, Stockholm
''Ex. 3.'' Frescati, south of Stora Skuggan

label: NormalStorageLocationText
definition: A text describing the normal physical storage location, in any chosen format.

label: OccurenceDateText
definition: A text describing the date of the Occurrence, in any chosen format.

label: PhysicalUnitText
definition: A text describing the PhysicalUnit, in any chosen format.
